node.text:
@DarrenCurtis_Christies sold this AUD $8,100,000 architectural home - A flawless example of contemporary oceanfront design, this exceptional residence merges striking forms and luxurious interior spaces to deliver a home of unparalleled beauty and simplicity. Unquestionably, one of the finest properties to be found on the Northern Beaches, its beachfront reserve position is just steps from the peninsula's most exclusive shoreline, basking in tremendous views across the sea and headlands. 

 Contact @DarrenCurtis_Christies for more information
